platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: vitez le trafic et les radars

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: People power meets the open road in this amazing navigation app. Wazes crowd-sourced alerts come from real drivers, not algorithms, delivering info you wont see anywhere else to keep your commute flowing. The friendly interface and convenient detour routing really help the app shine, and its social-network integration make road trips with buddies a blast.
